summary:
Currently writing a book on the history of Geijsteren Castle

former editor of Dutch art magazine 'Vormen uit Vuur'

author of a book on Dutch waterboard glass and curious habits connected with these glasses. Title: 't Welvaare van de Heere'.

speaker/announcer at international horse shows, concerts and events

Specialties: glass, especially drinking glasses for certain occasions, history, public speaking
